{"tid":1630112,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"屌你老母 叫撚咗幾多次企疏啲","createTime":"2019-10-06T11:28:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T14:45:26.000Z","uid":39338,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"5207abbc6b37dd94e01da6d251bf57993030113c","tid":1630112,"uid":39338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T11:28:54.000Z","msg":"灣仔班仆街陷家剷和理非<br />\n個撚個都無危機意識<br />\n無裝又要哄上前面睇<br />\n夠膽死 剩係戴住隻黑色口罩 <br />\n係咁lur 上前面<br />\n心諗你死返後面啦 <br />\n唔好阻撚住前線做野<br />\n我明你地想出一分力<br />\n但唔該 衡量返自己嘅能力同角色<br />\n<br />\n有啲情侶裝 拖撚住手隻上前睇<br />\n食撚屎啦屌你老母<br />\n班狗一推咪又係雞飛狗走<br />\n無心理準備就唔好企咁前啦<br />\n你地知唔知自己係現場做緊乜撚野呀？<br />\n你地知唔知今日累撚死幾多前線手足呀？<br />\n<br />\n講撚咗幾多次企疏啲<br />\n大家都仲要迫上去<br />\n今鋪完全係畀自己友累死<br />\n一大班豬隊友 唔該你地返去自己好好檢討下"},{"pid":"6f95a96b93efe22a20d9bcb57bebb13306dd2ee2","tid":1630112,"uid":39338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T11:37:42.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6ac103e634411f300382f5be3238deed7133a30b","tid":1630112,"uid":39338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T11:38:15.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"af85acff3f936cf52b1336ecb160a9382fa5d5d4","tid":1630112,"uid":39338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T11:38:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0e1cafffb771eabc684e93d322d3658aaa6d024c","tid":1630112,"uid":39338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T11:43:07.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"28cdd38eeacf1965db05fe3a232b81f2b3112bb2","tid":1630112,"uid":39338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T11:43:20.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1d4e193d9d079fc6123473de727f7e3f1f6402fa","tid":1630112,"uid":39338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T11:48:33.000Z","msg":"入黎同我懺悔"},{"pid":"f535cfa9e7e59c701f1c42ccb441c16e6f3f6f73","tid":1630112,"uid":39338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T11:49:19.000Z","msg":"入黎同我懺悔"},{"pid":"0f73499f298d21823671520783c0ca8f2c9fa2ea","tid":1